Install on Mac OSX

Download Mac installer
Double-click the .dmg file
Drag STViewer application icon to the Application folder
Start STViewer application from your Applications folder
(press CTRL to open it the first time it you get a message saying that the tool is not certified)

Install on Ubuntu

Download Ubuntu application package
Extract the archive to a location where you would like to store the program
To start the STViewer application open the Terminal at the extracted directory and type â€˜./STViewer

Install on Windows

Download Windows client installer
Double click on
Follow the instructions to install STViewer on your Windows machine
Search for STViewer on your applications folder and launch it
